oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jack Greene and Jeannie Seely and the Renegades at the Colonial Ballroom (18356)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Greene, Jack (Singer); Seely, Jeannie; Woodcuts (prints); Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing Jack Greene and Jeannie Seely and the Renegades at the Colonial Ballroom on January 22. Poster features a metal photoplate of Jack Greene and Jeannie Seely and woodcuts of stars. To see the business record associated with this poster, visit https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/42640/
